name: EYES OF PANDORA #3
description: EYES OF PANDORA #3 is my third Pandora's box. I engraved the panels with 6 different eyes to protect the treasure inside. The box #3 holds a song I wrote one year ago, when life was still easy and seemed predictable. Telling something that would be possible only in the dreams, I somehow predicted what happened next. You will be able to see it only if you download the OBJKT and watch inside the box. Always remind to protect the precious things, especially what marked a turning point in your lifeâ€™s trip.
